OL,3,CTeenage driver admits causing deaths
OL,4,Cof three passengers in two-car crash
OL,6,FA teenage motorist has admitted
OL,7,Fcausing the deaths of three passengers
OL,8,Fwho died in a two-car crash five weeks
OL,9,Fafter he passed his driving test.
OL,11,FWarwickshire Police said the case of
OL,12,FEdward Spencer, aged 19, showed the
OL,13,F"devastating consequences" that can
OL,14,Foccur if a car is driven carelessly.
