OL,3,CTeenage driver admits causing deaths
OL,4,Cof three passengers in two-car crash
OL,6,FSpencer, of Armscote Road, Newbold on
OL,7,FStour, pleaded guilty at Warwick Crown
OL,8,FCourt on Monday to three counts of
OL,9,Fcausing death by careless driving and
OL,10,Fthree counts of causing serious injury
OL,11,Fby careless driving in a crash between
OL,12,FChipping Campden and Shipston-on-Stour
OL,13,Fin April 2023.
OL,15,FPolice said Spencer lost control of
OL,16,Fhis car on the B4035 Campden Road
OL,17,Fwhile on his way home from school.
