OL,3,CTeenage driver admits causing deaths
OL,4,Cof three passengers in two-car crash
OL,6,FFollowing the collision, 17-year-old
OL,7,FHarry Purcell, 16-year-old Tilly
OL,8,FSeccombe and 16-year-old Frank
OL,9,FWormald, who were passengers in
OL,10,FSpencer's Ford Fiesta, died as a
OL,11,Fresult of their injuries.
OL,13,FA woman and two young children, who
OL,14,Fwere travelling in another car, were
OL,15,Fseriously injured and are receiving
OL,16,Ftreatment in hospital for life-
OL,17,Fchanging injuries.
