OL,3,CTeenage driver admits causing deaths
OL,4,Cof three passengers in two-car crash
OL,6,FInspector Michael Huntley, from the
OL,7,FWarwickshire Police Serious Collision
OL,8,FInvestigation Unit, urged young people
OL,9,Fand their parents to consider the
OL,10,Flimitations of being a newly-qualified
OL,11,Fdriver.
OL,13,FHe said: "Drivers need to be aware of
OL,14,Fthe devastating consequences that can
OL,15,Foccur if a car is driven carelessly.
OL,17,F"Edward Spencer had only passed his
OL,18,Ftest five weeks prior to the collision
OL,19,Fand his careless actions cost the
OL,20,Flives of three young people travelling
OL,21,Fin his car.
