OL,3,CTeenage driver admits causing deaths
OL,4,Cof three passengers in two-car crash
OL,6,F"Driving requires judgment and care,
OL,7,Feven more so when you lack experience.
OL,8,FAs this tragic case shows, the
OL,9,Fconsequences of careless driving can
OL,10,Fbe devastating.
OL,12,F"So many lives have been ruined by
OL,13,Fthis terrible incident. I can't begin
OL,14,Fto imagine the pain this has caused,
OL,15,Fand our thoughts remain with the
OL,16,Findividuals and families affected.
OL,18,F"Edward Spencer will live with the
OL,19,Fconsequences of his careless actions
OL,20,Ffor the rest of his life, as will the
OL,21,Ffamilies of all those involved."
