OL,6,FShortly after the crash, Chipping
OL,7,FCampden School in Gloucestershire paid
OL,8,Ftribute to the students who lost their
OL,9,Flives, who were all members of its
OL,10,Fsixth form.
OL,12,FSpencer was granted bail and will be
OL,13,Fsentenced on April 28.
